            SIPS 2021 Lightening talk
          Thoughts about language psychology studiesOn which facts language psychologists confirm their theories/models?

Language effects: Responses between some language aspects
Factorial design by language aspects: word frequency, prime-target relation, sentence structures, …
Manipulations on the language aspects vibrated within/between languages.

Why are language studies less reproducible?

Within language: Effects varied with the selected materials
Between languages: Language A detected that effect, but Language B failed.

Challenges afterwardPSA 002: a global investigation on orientation effects across languages.
Orientation effect implied how human comprehend the sentences based on visual experience.
Most accumulated data came from English, and the results showed the weak effect (~ 10 ms).
PSA 002 Meta websiteBoost meta-analysis on orientation effect across languages
Easier reproduction

